#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:4
msgid "afp_logintest — AFP authentication and DSI session test suite"
msgstr "afp_logintest — AFP認証とDSIセッションテストスイート"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "**afp_logintest** [-1234567CmVv] [-f *test*] [-h *host*] [-p *port*] [-s *volume*] [-u *user*] [-w *password*]\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "**afp_logintest** -l\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**afp_logintest** is a testsuite for DSI sessions and authentication from an AFP client.\n"
"It will run a range of happy path and corner case tests for establishing a DSI session\n"
"with an AFP server and then use UAMs (User Authentication Methods) to authenticate with a user.\n"
msgstr ""
"**afp_logintest** は、DSIセッションとAFPクライアントからの認証のためのテストスイートである。\n"
"AFPサーバーとのDSIセッションを確立するための様々なハッピーパステストとコーナーケーステストを実行し、\n"
"利用可能なUAM（ユーザ認証メソッド）を使用してユーザー認証を行う。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:21 manpages/man1/afp_spectest.1.md:24
#: manpages/man1/afp_speedtest.1.md:31 manpages/man1/afparg.1.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**-1**\n"
": Use AFP 2.1 protocol version\n"
msgstr ""
"**-1**\n"
": AFP 2.1プロトコルバージョンを使用する\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:24 manpages/man1/afp_spectest.1.md:27
#: manpages/man1/afp_speedtest.1.md:34 manpages/man1/afparg.1.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**-2**\n"
": Use AFP 2.2 protocol version\n"
msgstr ""
"**-2**\n"
": AFP 2.2プロトコルバージョンを使用する\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:42 manpages/man1/afp_spectest.1.md:51
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**-C**\n"
": Turn off ANSI colors in terminal output\n"
msgstr ""
"**-C**\n"
": 端末出力でANSIカラーをオフにする\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:45
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**-f** *test*\n"
": Run a specific test\n"
msgstr ""
"**-f** *test*\n"
": 実行するテストを指定する\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:51
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**-l**\n"
": List available tests\n"
msgstr ""
"**-l**\n"
": 利用可能なすべてのテストを一覧表示する\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:54 manpages/man1/afp_spectest.1.md:77
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**-m**\n"
": Run tests in AppleShare (Mac) AFP server compatibility mode\n"
msgstr ""
"**-m**\n"
": AppleShare (Mac) AFP サーバー互換モードでテストを実行する\n"

#. type: Title #
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "Preconditions"
msgstr "前提条件"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:75
msgid ""
"In order to test Guest and Clear Text authentication, netatalk must be "
"configured to use the *uams_guest* and *uams_clrtxt.so* UAMs, respectively.  "
"Configure the UAMs in netatalk's afp.conf:"
msgstr ""
"ゲスト認証とクリアテキスト認証をテストするには、それぞれ *uams_guest* と "
"*uams_clrtxt.so* UAM を使用するように netatalk を設定する必要がある。下記事例"
"の通り、netatalk の afp.conf で UAM を設定する。"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:78 manpages/man1/afp_spectest.1.md:217
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    [Global]\n"
"    uam list = uams_clrtxt.so uams_guest.so\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:81
msgid ""
"Other tests may require additional UAMs to be configured; see the test "
"output for details on which tests failed due to missing UAMs."
msgstr ""
"その他のテストでは、追加のUAMを設定する必要がある場合がある。どのテストがUAM"
"の不足のために失敗したかの詳細については、テスト出力を参照すること。"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:83
msgid ""
"Additionally, in order to test non-Guest authentication, a username and "
"password must be passed to the test runner."
msgstr ""
"さらに、非ゲスト認証をテストするには、ユーザー名とパスワードをテストランナー"
"に渡す必要がある。"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:87
msgid ""
"Run all tests against an AFP server running on 10.0.0.10, without user "
"credentials"
msgstr ""
"10.0.0.10で実行されているAFPサーバーに対して、ユーザー認証なしですべてのテス"
"トを実行する。"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    $ afp_logintest -h 10.0.0.10\n"
"    Logintest:test1: DSI with no open session - PASSED\n"
"    Logintest:test2: DSI with open session - PASSED\n"
"    Logintest:test3: Guest login - PASSED\n"
"    Logintest:test4: connection limit hit returns server-busy - PASSED\n"
"    Logintest:test5: Clear text login - SKIPPED (username/password for the AFP server)\n"
"    Logintest:test6: DSIOpenSession non zero parameter should be ignored by the server - SKIPPED (username/password for the AFP server)\n"
"    Logintest:test7: DSI round-trip via renamed dsi_stream_send/dsi_cmd_receive - PASSED\n"
"    Logintest:test8: FPLoginExt + No User Authent (direct) - PASSED\n"
"    Logintest:test9: AFPLoginCont primitive round-trip - SKIPPED (username/password for the AFP server)\n"
"    Logintest:test10: UAM matrix walk - PASSED\n"
"    =====================\n"
"    TEST RESULT SUMMARY\n"
"    ---------------------\n"
"    Passed:     7\n"
"    Skipped:    3\n"
"    Failed:     0\n"
"    Not tested: 0\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:111
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    Skipped tests (precondition not met):\n"
"        Logintest:test5: Clear text login\n"
"        Logintest:test6: DSIOpenSession non zero parameter should be ignored by the server\n"
"        Logintest:test9: AFPLoginCont primitive round-trip\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_logintest.1.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "**afp_lantest**(1), **afp_spectest**(1), **afparg**(1), **afpd**(8)\n"
msgstr ""
